Class SentencePair

java.lang.Object
  edu.jhu.coe.mt.SentencePair
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SentencePair
extends Object
implements Serializable

A holder for a pair of sentences, each a list of strings. Sentences in the test sets have integer IDs, as well, which are used to retreive the gold standard alignments for those sentences.
